IMAPAccount bbo
Host imap.gmail.com
User naoki@bbo.cs.tsukuba.ac.jp
PassCmd "cat ~/src/github.com/naoking158/envs/.bbo-mail-pw"
Port 993
SSLType IMAPS
AuthMechs PLAIN
# CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore bbo-remote
Account bbo

MaildirStore bbo-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/Mail/BBO/
Inbox ~/Mail/BBO/Inbox

Channel bbo
Far :bbo-remote:
Near :bbo-local:
Patterns INBOX *Gmail* ![Gmail]/Spam
# Patterns "Inbox" "Starred" "Sent" "Drafts" "Trash" "Important" "Spam"
Create Both
SyncState *


